2026-07-21T04:24:01.3264867Z [36;1m# 1) Canonical Docker Hub. The common transient-blip case recovers here.[0m
2026-07-21T04:24:01.3265217Z [36;1mif pull_with_retries "${BUILDKIT_IMAGE}"; then[0m
2026-07-21T04:24:01.3265629Z [36;1m  echo "==> BuildKit image cached locally from canonical registry; boot will not need a registry pull"[0m
